snippet.title: Amber Heard called Johnny Depp 'pathetic' after he passed out eating ice cream
snippet.description: Amber Heard told   "look what you've become" and branded him "pathetic" after he passed out while eating ice cream.  The photo shows the actor asleep on a sofa with a tub of melted ice cream in his lap, and was show in court today as part of Depp's libel case against News Group Newspapers.  Depp, 57, is suing NGN over a story published in The Sun in 201 which branded him a "wife beater" - a claim which he strenuously denies.  The Pirates of The Caribbean star returned to the witness stand this morning for his final round of testimony.  He was questioned over whether his ex-wife Heard had shown him any pictures of injuries she's eged to have sustained during their relationship.  Depp's lawyer said it had been suggested by Heard that she had started taking pictures and videos of her injuries so she could show Depp what he had done to her the next morning because he would not be able to remember details of their fights.   He asked Depp if she had ever shown him any of the photos before t ...
